Comment.value:
1) once the brazier is destroyed, set the 'Freeing_Nyphithys' global on Nyphithys to 3.  Have her display a 'Ahh...good.' line.
2) when the 'Freeing_Nyphithys' global is set to 1 or 2, start a timer for 2 minutes real time. If the player has not destroyed
the brazier as above, she should display this line and go hostile: "Enough! I have waited long enough for you to complete a
simple task!"
3) when Nyphithys goes hostile, she uses the 2Q6_NYPHITHYS03 script. It will have to polymorph her into succubus form.
The same thing should occur if she is attacked while in human form.
4) Unless the brazier has been destroyed, Nyphithys cannot leave the room she's in.
5) 2Q6_NYPHITHYS11 script will need to be edited to add the item reward she gives, as well as have her teleport away permanently
